  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[When Digivolving] Reveal the top 3 cards of your deck.
    Add 1 card with [Alphamon] in its name among them to your hand, and place 1 card
    with [X Antibody] in its traits among them under this Digimon as its bottom digivolution
    card. Trash the rest.'
